skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Listen daily to Heather Warner with the Alicia Holmes Team giving you new home listings in the Lee's Summit area. With this competitive home buying market find your next home faster with this flash briefing.

If you are interested in specific suggestions for your home buying search we can create you your own custom skill to listen to daily to find new homes suited for you that have hit our local market. Please email at heatherwarner@kw.com or text/call me at 479-366-2929 if you would like your own custom Alexa Skill.

The Alicia Holmes team is apart of Keller Williams Realty Partners.
